title: SET_VEHICLE_MISSILE_WARNING_ENABLED
content:
0xF3365489E0DD50F90x8AFC488D// SetVehicleMissileWarningEnabled
void SET_VEHICLE_MISSILE_WARNING_ENABLED(Vehicle vehicle, BOOL toggle);Parameters:vehicle: Vehicle to toggle warning system for.toggle: true to enable, false to disable.Toggles the incoming missile warning system for specified vehicle.
codeBlocks:
local ped = PlayerPedId()
local vehicle = GetVehiclePedIsIn(ped, false)
-- Example usage for SET_VEHICLE_MISSILE_WARNING_ENABLED
SetVehicleMissileWarningEnabled(vehicle, false)
